3. **leukemia heterogeneity** = AML/ALL/CML/CLL 각자 별도 mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 mechanism-specific design 가능.
4. **voxelotor 2024 withdrawal** = post-marketing safety; quantum-VQE evidence 가 임상 efficacy 보장 X 명확 case.
5. **emicizumab bispecific** = factor VIII mimetic, large-protein bispecific Ab. small-molecule alternative 가능성.
6. **sickle cell socioeconomic** = global burden + access issue. quantum-design 외부.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, heme 임상 의미 한정.

